	 <h4 class="header">Characteristic Species</h4>
	<div class="text"> <i>Agropyron</i> <i>cristatum</i> is dominant in the herbaceous layer. Emergent trees and shrubs may be present at low cover. </div>
</div>

        
	
<div class="allianceSection">
	 <h4 class="header">Vegetation Layers</h4>
	<div class="text">  Herbs < 1 m; cover is open. </div>
</div>

        
<div class="allianceSection">
	 <h4 class="header">Membership Rules</h4>
	<ul class="text">
		
		<li><i>Agropyron cristatum</i> > 50% relative cover and native plants generally < 10% relative cover in the herbaceous layer (NatureServe 2007).</li>
		
	</ul>
</div>

        
	
